Package: sshpiperd
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 adduser
Recommends: sshpiperd-plugins
Description: SSH reverse proxy / connection router
 sshpiperd routes incoming SSH connections to upstream servers based on
 pluggable logic. Useful for bastion hosts, multi-tenant gateways, and
 per-user routing without shell accounts on the proxy itself.

Package: sshpiperd-plugins
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 sshpiperd (= ${binary:Version})
Description: sshpiperd bundled upstream plugins
 Ships the gRPC-capable upstream plugins (workingdir, yaml, ldap, etc.)
 built from the sshpiper source tree. Install alongside sshpiperd to
 enable plugin-based routing.
